The,Freightview,API,allow,developers,to,pull,n,LTL,freight,rates,into,an,application,or,website,Freightview,requires,an,account,to,be,set,up,to,use,their,API,Other,features,include,the,ability,to,retrieve,rates,schedule,pickups,and,track,from,pickup,to,delivery,The,Freightview,tool,shows,a,user,all,of,their,freight,carriers,with,their,rates,all,on,one,screen